# Anki Card Creation HTTP Request (Example)
# Store your real Bearer token in .env.test or .env.local (git-ignored).
# Use environment variables: {{API_BASE_URL}}, {{API_PASSWORD}}

### Create Card
POST {{API_BASE_URL}}/api/anki/cards
Accept: application/json, text/plain, */*
Authorization: Bearer {{API_PASSWORD}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "front": "werken",
  "back": "to work",
  "notes": "Common verb",
  "deck_id": "{{DECK_ID}}",
  "tags": ["verb", "common"]
}

### Example env
# API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5055
# API_PASSWORD=6596011
# DECK_ID=anki_deck:xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
